# Environment Variables (if needed in the future)

# This project doesn't currently require environment variables.
# Add any environment variables needed for your deployment here.

# Example:
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.example.com
# VITE_APP_NAME=Ferrari Redesign

# Note: Variables starting with VITE_ are exposed to the client-side.
